---
const title = "JavaScript 공부 기록";
const date = "2026.07.19";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{title} | hiJay97</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="article-window">
      <header class="toolbar">
        <div class="traffic">
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
        </div>

        <a href="/">← Home</a>
      </header>

      <article>
  <p class="date">{date}</p>
  <h1>{title}</h1>

  <p>
    오늘은 JavaScript의 비동기 처리에 대해 공부했습니다.
  </p>

  <h2>Promise란?</h2>

  <p>
    Promise는 비동기 작업의 결과를 나타내는 객체입니다.
  </p>
</article>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    min-height: 100vh;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 48px 20px;
    color: #f5f5f7;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, #26334a, transparent 38rem),
      #090a0d;
    font-family:
      -apple-system,
      BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Apple SD Gothic Neo",
      sans-serif;
  }

  .article-window {
    width: min(900px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: rgba(28, 29, 34, 0.92);
    box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  }

  .toolbar {
    display: flex;
    min-height: 56px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
  }

  .toolbar a {
    color: #0a84ff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .traffic {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .traffic span {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .traffic span:nth-child(1) {
    background: #ff5f57;
  }

  .traffic span:nth-child(2) {
    background: #febc2e;
  }

  .traffic span:nth-child(3) {
    background: #28c840;
  }

  article {
    padding: clamp(32px, 7vw, 72px);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 10px 0 28px;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 7vw, 64px);
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
  }

  p {
    color: #b5b5ba;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .date {
    color: #0a84ff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>